    <item>
      <title>前 FTX、Alameda 员工收购破产公司的欧洲实体</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/former-ftx-alameda-staff-at-backpack-acquires-failed-firm-s-european-entity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Backpack Exchange 是一个加密货币交易平台，由 Sam Bankman-Fried 的 FTX 和 Alameda Research 企业的一次性员工创立，该平台以 3270 万美元收购了破产的 FTX 交易所的前欧洲实体，以扩大其在该地区的衍生品产品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/former-ftx-alameda-staff-at-backpack-acquires-failed-firm-s-european-entity</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>MicroStrategy 在增加优先认购权后购买比特币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/microstrategy-buys-bitcoin-after-adding-preferred-stock-offering</link>
      <description><![CDATA[MicroStrategy Inc. 宣布将使用永久优先股以及普通股和债务来购买更多加密货币，随后购买了价值 1.01 亿美元的比特币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/microstrategy-buys-bitcoin-after-adding-preferred-stock-offering</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 13:12:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着全球风险反弹的恢复，比特币重新夺回 100,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/bitcoin-btc-approaches-100-000-as-congress-set-to-certify-trump-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于 2025 年第一个完整交易周开始时股市上涨，提振了对风险较高资产的需求，比特币两周来首次突破 100,000 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/bitcoin-btc-approaches-100-000-as-congress-set-to-certify-trump-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 09:15:53 GMT</pubDate>
